      "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. By the zero-product property, if <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, x minus 4, close parenthesis, times, open parenthesis, x plus 2, close parenthesis, times, open parenthesis, x minus 1, close parenthesis, equals 0\"></span>, then <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x minus 4, equals 0\"></span>, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x plus 2, equals 0\"></span>, or <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x minus 1, equals 0\"></span>. Solving each of these equations for <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x\"></span> yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals 4\"></span>, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals negative 2\"></span>, or <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals 1\"></span>. The product of these solutions is <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"4 times negative 2, times 1, equals negative 8\"></span>.<p>Choice A is incorrect and may result from sign errors made when solving the given equation. Choice B is incorrect and may result from finding the sum, not the product, of the solutions. Choice C is incorrect and may result from finding the sum, not the product, of the solutions in addition to making sign errors